Class Slot.SlotContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codename1.rad.ui.Slot.SlotContext
  • Enclosing class:
    Slot

    public static class Slot.SlotContext
extends Object

    Encapsulates a context for a Slot. This includes all of the information to know how to build views inside this slot.
